name: Curtis Busch
description: I`m romantic/optimistic, considerate, outgoing person, warm in nature and very creative. I like to say what I feel and what I think…I don`t like to keep my opinion just in my mind…I do like to speak about everything. I`m intellectual, emotional, confident person and I have a sense of humor, I like to laugh and have fun. I like to spend time at the gym, swim/sunbathe, hike, tennis…wine tasting, fine dining, shopping, traveling, spa…
